source: Il y a de nombreuses choses à prendre en considération avant et pendant que vous voyagez.
reference: There are many things you have to take into consideration before and when you travel somewhere.
translation: There are many things to consider before and during your trip.

source: Lorsque vous voyagez, attendez-vous à ce que les choses ne soient pas comme « chez vous ». Les manières, les lois, la nourriture, la circulation, le logement, les normes, la langue, etc. diffèrent dans une certaine mesure de l’endroit où vous vivez.
reference: When you travel, expect things not to be like they are "back home". Manners, laws, food, traffic, lodging, standards, language and so on will to some extent differ from where you live.
translation: When you travel, expect things to be different from "where you live." The laws, customs, food, traffic, housing, norms, language, etc. vary a little in a certain way from where you live.

source: C'est quelque chose que vous devez toujours garder à l'esprit pour éviter toute déception ou peut-être même toute aversion à l'égard des comportements locaux.
reference: This is something you always need to keep in mind, to avoid disappointment or perhaps even distaste over local ways to do things.
translation: This is something you should always keep in mind when you are trying to avoid any disappointment or even any discomfort with the local behavior.

source: Les agences de voyage existent depuis le XIXe siècle. Un voyagiste est généralement une bonne option pour un périple qui dépasse le cadre des expériences précédentes du voyageur en matière de nature, culture, langue, ou pays à faible revenu.
reference: Travel agencies have been around since the 19th century. A travel agent is usually a good option for a journey which extends beyond a traveller's previous experience of nature, culture, language or low-income countries.
translation: Travel agencies exist since the 19th century. A traveller usually chooses a good option for a trip that exceeds the experience of previous travelers in nature, culture, language, or country with low income.

source: Bien que la plupart des agences soient disposées à prendre en charge la plupart des réservations régulières, de nombreux agents sont spécialisés dans des types de voyages, des gammes de prix ou des destinations plus spécifiques.
reference: Although most agencies are willing to take on most regular bookings, many agents specialise in particular types of travel, budget ranges or destinations.
translation: Although most agencies are willing to take most regular bookings, many agents are specialized in a type of travel, a price range, or a specific destination.

source: Il peut être préférable de faire appel à un agent qui réserve fréquemment des voyages similaires au vôtre.
reference: It can be better to use an agent who frequently books similar trips to yours.
translation: It may be better to hire a travel agent who frequently book similar trips to yours.

source: Jetez un coup d’œil aux voyages dont l’agent fait la promotion, que ce soit sur un site internet ou en vitrine.
reference: Take a look at what trips the agent is promoting, whether on a website or in a shop window.
translation: Look at the travel agents who promote the trips, either online or in a store.

source: Si vous voulez voir le monde à bas prix, par nécessité, mode de vie ou défi, il existe quelques moyens de le faire.
reference: If you want to see the world on the cheap, for necessity, lifestyle or challenge, there are some ways to do that.
translation: If you want to see the world at a low cost, necessity, lifestyle or challenge, there are some ways to do it.

source: En gros, on peut les classer en deux catégories : soit vous travaillez pendant votre voyage, soit vous essayez de limiter vos dépenses. Le présent article porte essentiellement sur cette dernière catégorie.
reference: Basically, they fall into two categories: Either work while you travel or try and limit your expenses. This article is focused on the latter.
translation: Basically, you can classify them into two categories: either you work while you're traveling, or you try to limit your expenses. The article is mainly about this category.

source: Pour ceux qui sont prêts à sacrifier le confort, le temps et la prévisibilité pour réduire les dépenses à près de zéro, consultez le voyage à budget minimum.
reference: For those willing to sacrifice comfort, time and predictability to push expenses down close to zero, see minimum budget travel.
translation: For those who are willing to sacrifice comfort, time and predictability for the sake of reducing expenses to a minimum, check out the budget travel.

source: Ces conseils partent du principe que les voyageurs ne volent pas, ne s’introduisent pas dans un lieu public, ne participent pas au marché illégal, ne mendient pas ou n’exploitent pas d’autres personnes à leur profit.
reference: The advice assumes that travellers do not steal, trespass, participate in the illegal market, beg, or otherwise exploit other people for their own gain.
translation: These advice are based on the premise that travellers do not steal, enter into public spaces, participate in illegal markets, mend or exploit other people for their own gain.

source: Un point de contrôle d'immigration est habituellement la première étape lorsque vous débarquez d'un avion, d'un bateau ou d'un autre véhicule.
reference: An immigration checkpoint is usually the first stop when disembarking from a plane, a ship, or another vehicle.
translation: A checkpoint is usually the first stop on a plane, boat, or other vehicle when you arrive in a country.

source: Dans certains trains transfrontaliers, les inspections sont menées dans le train en marche et vous devez avoir une pièce d'identité valide sur vous lorsque vous voyagez dans l'un de ces trains.
reference: In some cross-border trains inspections are done on the running train and you should have valid ID with you when boarding one of those trains.
translation: In some cross-border trains, inspections are carried out in the running train and you must have a valid passport when you travel in one of these trains.

source: Dans les trains-couchettes qui roulent de nuit, les passeports peuvent être collectés par le chef de train afin de ne pas interrompre votre sommeil.
reference: On night sleeper trains, passports may be collected by the conductor so that you do not have your sleep interrupted.
translation: In the train cabins that sleep on the night, passports can be collected by the train captain to prevent you from sleeping.

source: L’enregistrement est une exigence supplémentaire pour la procédure de visa. Dans certains pays, vous devez vous faire enregistrer et indiquer l’adresse de votre lieu de séjour auprès des autorités locales.
reference: Registration is an additional requirement for the visa process. In some countries, you must register your presence and address where you are staying with the local authorities.
translation: The recording is a requirement for the visa process. In some countries, you must register and indicate your place of stay in the local authorities.

source: Cela peut nécessiter de remplir un formulaire auprès de la police locale ou une visite aux bureaux de l'immigration.
reference: This might require filling out a form with the local police or a visit to the immigration offices.
translation: This can require filling out a form with the local police or a visit to the immigration office.

source: Dans beaucoup de pays disposant d'une telle loi, les hôtels locaux s'occuperont eux-mêmes de l'enregistrement (n'oubliez pas de demander).
reference: In many countries with such a law, local hotels will handle the registration (make sure to ask).
translation: In many countries with such a law, local hotels will handle the registration (don't forget to ask).

source: Dans d'autres cas, seules les personnes résidant hors hébergements touristiques doivent s'enregistrer. Toutefois, la loi est beaucoup plus obscure, donc il conviendra de se renseigner au préalable.
reference: In other cases, only those staying outside of tourist accommodations need to register.  However, this makes the law much more obscure, so find out beforehand.
translation: In other cases, only people residing in non-threatening hotels should register. However, the law is much more obscure, so you should be aware of the rules beforehand.

source: L'architecture se rapporte à la conception et à la construction des bâtiments. L'architecture d'un site est souvent une attraction touristique à part entière.
reference: Architecture is concerned with the design and construction of buildings. The architecture of a place is often a tourist attraction in its own right.
translation: Architecture relates to the design and construction of buildings. Architecture of a site is often a tourist attraction in itself.

source: De nombreux bâtiments sont plutôt agréables à regarder, et la vue qu'offrent les grands bâtiments ou des fenêtres savamment placées peut être d'une beauté saisissante.
reference: Many buildings are quite beautiful to look at and the view from a tall building or from a cleverly-positioned window can be a beauty to behold.
translation: Many buildings are pleasant to look at, and the view from the large buildings or windows placed carefully can be of a beauty that is astonishing.

source: L’architecture recoupe considérablement d’autres domaines, notamment l’urbanisme, le génie civil, les arts décoratifs, la décoration intérieure et l’aménagement paysager.
reference: Architecture overlaps considerably with other fields including urban planning, civil engineering, decorative arts, interior design and landscape design.
translation: Architecture is closely related to other fields, such as urban planning, civil engineering, decorative arts, interior design and landscaping.

source: Étant donné l’éloignement de nombreux pueblos, vous ne pourrez pas trouver une vie nocturne importante sans vous rendre à Albuquerque ou à Santa Fe.
reference: Given how remote many of the pueblos are, you won't be able to find a significant amount of nightlife without traveling to Albuquerque or Santa Fe.
translation: Due to the distance between many pueblos, you will not be able to find a large nightlife without going to Albuquerque or Santa Fe.

source: Toutefois, presque tous les casinos cités ci-dessus servent des boissons, et plusieurs d'entre eux proposent des distractions de haute qualité (principalement les grands casinos situés à proximité d'Albuquerque et de Santa Fe)
reference: However, nearly all of the casinos listed above serve drinks, and several of them bring in name-brand entertainment (primarily the large ones immediately surrounding Albuquerque and Santa Fe).
translation: However, almost all casinos listed above serve drinks, and several of them offer high quality entertainment (mainly the large casinos near Albuquerque and Santa Fe).

source: Méfiez-vous : les bars des petites villes ici ne sont pas toujours de bons endroits pour traîner si vous êtes visiteur étranger.
reference: Beware: small-town bars here are not always good places for the out-of-state visitor to hang out.
translation: Beware: bars in small towns here are not always good places to hang out if you're a tourist.

source: D'une part, le nord du Nouveau-Mexique connaît des problèmes importants de conduite en état d'ivresse, et la concentration de conducteurs en état d'ébriété est élevée à proximité des bars des petites villes.
reference: For one thing, northern New Mexico has significant problems with drunk driving, and the concentration of intoxicated drivers is high close to small-town bars.
translation: First, the north of the United States has serious problems in driving in the state of intoxication, and the concentration of intoxicated drivers is high near bars in small towns.

source: Les peintures murales ou les gribouillages indésirables sont connus sous le nom de graffitis.
reference: Unwanted murals or scribble is known as graffiti.
translation: Painted murals or graffiti are known as graffiti.

source: Bien que ce soit loin d'être un phénomène moderne, la plupart des gens l'associent probablement au fait que des jeunes vandalisent des propriétés publiques et privées en utilisant de la peinture en aérosol.
reference: While it's far from a modern phenomenon, most people probably associate it with youth vandalizing public and private property using spray paint.
translation: Although this is not a modern phenomenon, most people associate it with the fact that young vandals use paint aerosol to vandalize property.

source: Il existe toutefois aujourd'hui des graffeurs reconnus, des événements consacrés à la discipline et des surfaces « autorisées » pour s'y adonner. Dans ces conditions, les graffitis ressemblent plus souvent à de véritables œuvres d'art qu'à de vulgaires tags indéchiffrables.
reference: However, nowadays there are established graffiti artists, graffiti events and "legal" walls. Graffiti paintings in this context often resemble artworks rather than illegible tags.
translation: However, graffiti is still recognized today, graffiti events are held, and graffiti surfaces are "allowed." In these conditions, graffiti is more likely to resemble real art than a tag that is not readable.

source: Le lancer de Boomerang est une compétence populaire que de nombreux touristes veulent acquérir.
reference: Boomerang throwing is a popular skill that many tourists want to acquire.
translation: Boomerang throwing is a popular skill that many tourists want to acquire.

source: Si vous voulez apprendre à lancer un boomerang qui vous retourne directement dans la main, alors assurez-vous de bien avoir un boomerang conçu pour revenir.
reference: If you want to learn throwing a boomerang that comes back to your hand, make sure you have a suitable boomerang for returning.
translation: If you want to learn how to throw a boomerang that returns directly to your hand, then ensure that you have a boomerang designed to return.

source: En réalité, la plupart des boomerangs disponibles en Australie ne reviennent pas. Il est préférable pour les débutants de ne pas essayer de faire de lancers dans le vent.
reference: Most boomerangs available in Australia are in fact non-returning. It is best for beginners to not try throwing in windy
translation: In fact, most available boomerangs in Australia don't return. It is better for beginners to not try to hit the wind.

source: On cuit un repas hangi dans une fosse chaude creusée dans le sol.
reference: A Hangi Meal is cooked in a hot pit in the ground.
translation: A hangi meal is cooked in a hot pit in the ground.

source: La fosse est soit chauffée avec des pierres chaudes provenant d'un feu, soit la chaleur géothermique réchauffe naturellement certaines zones du sol.
reference: The pit is either heated with hot stones from a fire, or in some places geothermal heat makes areas of ground naturally hot.
translation: The pit is either heated with hot stones from a fire, or the heat of geothermal heat is naturally absorbed in some areas of the soil.

source: Le hangi est souvent utilisé pour préparer un dîner traditionnel de type rôti.
reference: The hangi is often used to cook a traditional roast style dinner.
translation: Hangi is often used to prepare traditional dinner type roast.

source: Plusieurs endroits à Rotorua offrent des hangis géothermiques, tandis que d’autres hangis peuvent être échantillonnés à Christchurch, Wellington et ailleurs.
reference: Several places in Rotorua offer geothermal hangi, while other hangi can be sampled in Christchurch, Wellington and elsewhere.
translation: Several places in Rotorua offer geothermal hangi, while others can be sampled in Christchurch, Wellington and elsewhere.

source: MetroRail propose deux classes dans les trains de banlieue du Cap et de ses environs : MetroPlus (également appelée première classe) et Metro (appelée troisième classe).
reference: MetroRail has two classes on commuter trains in and around Cape Town: MetroPlus (also called First Class) and Metro (called Third Class).
translation: MetroRail offers two classes in the Cap and its environs: MetroPlus (also called first class) and Metro (called third class).

source: MetroPlus est plus confortable et moins bondé, mais plus cher, tout en restant moins cher que le tarif normal des billets de métro en Europe.
reference: MetroPlus is more comfortable and less crowded but slightly more expensive, though still cheaper than normal metro tickets in Europe.
translation: MetroPlus is more comfortable and less crowded, but more expensive, but still cheaper than normal metro tickets in Europe.

source: Chaque train dispose de wagons Metro et MetroPlus ; les wagons MetroPlus sont toujours en bout du train le plus proche du Cap.
reference: Every train has both MetroPlus and Metro coaches; the MetroPlus coaches are always on the end of the train nearest Cape Town.
translation: Each train has a Metro and MetroPlus; the MetroPlus always comes closest to the Cap.

source: Porter pour les autres – ne perdez jamais vos sacs de vue, surtout lorsque vous traversez des frontières internationales.
reference: Carrying for others - Never let your bags out of your sight, especially when you are crossing international borders.
translation: The other way around: Don't ever lose your sight of your bags, especially when crossing borders.

source: Quelqu'un pourrait se servir de vous pour transporter de la drogue à votre insu, ce qui vous attirerait de gros ennuis.
reference: You could find yourself being used as a drug carrier without your knowledge, which will land you in a great deal of trouble.
translation: Someone might use you to transport drugs to your insu, which would be a big problem for you.

source: Cela inclut l'attente en ligne, car les chiens renifleurs de drogue peuvent être utilisés à tout moment sans préavis.
reference: This includes waiting in line, as drug-sniffing dogs could be used at any time without notice.
translation: This includes the waiting time, as dogs that smell drugs can be used at any time without notice.

source: Dans certains pays, les sanctions sont extrêmement draconiennes, même pour les premières infractions ; elles peuvent aller jusqu'à des peines de prison de plus de dix ans ou la peine de mort.
reference: Some countries have exceedingly draconian punishments even for first time offenses; these can include prison sentences of over 10 years or death.
translation: In some countries, sanctions are extremely harsh, even for the first offenses; they can be up to 10 years in prison or death.

source: Les sacs sans surveillance sont une cible pour le vol et peuvent également attirer l'attention des autorités qui se méfient des alertes à la bombe.
reference: Unattended bags are a target for theft and can also attract attention from authorities wary of bomb threats.
translation: The bags without surveillance are a target for theft and can also attract the attention of authorities who are suspicious of the alert to bomb.

source: À la maison, en raison de cette exposition constante aux germes locaux, les chances sont très élevées que vous soyez déjà immunisé contre eux.
reference: At home, due to this constant exposure to the local germs, odds are very high that you're already immune to them.
translation: At home, due to this constant exposure to local germs, the chances are very high that you already have been immunized against them.

source: Mais dans d'autres parties du monde, où la faune bactériologique est nouvelle pour vous, vous risquez bien plus de rencontrer des problèmes.
reference: But in other parts of the world, where the bacteriological fauna are new to you, you're far more likely to run into problems.
translation: But in other parts of the world where the bacteriological fauna is new to you, you may be more likely to encounter problems.

source: De plus, dans les climats plus chauds, les bactéries se développent plus rapidement et survivent plus longtemps à l'extérieur du corps.
reference: Also, in warmer climates bacteria both grow more quickly and survive longer outside the body.
translation: In warmer climates, bacteria grow more quickly and survive longer outside the body.

source: Ainsi les fléaux de Delhi Belly, la malédiction du pharaon, la vengeance de Montezuma et leurs nombreux amis.
reference: Thus the scourges of Delhi Belly, the Pharaoh's Curse, Montezuma's Revenge, and their many friends.
translation: Thus the plague of Delhi Belly, the curse of Pharaoh, the vengeance of Montezuma and their many friends.

source: Comme pour les problèmes respiratoires dans les climats plus froids, les problèmes intestinaux dans les climats chauds sont assez courants et, dans la plupart des cas, sont particulièrement gênants mais pas vraiment dangereux.
reference: As with respiratory problems in colder climates, intestinal problems in hot climates are fairly common and in most cases are distinctly annoying but not really dangerous.
translation: As for respiratory problems in cold climates, intestinal problems in hot climates are fairly common and, in the majority of cases, are quite annoying but not really dangerous.

source: Si vous voyagez pour la première fois dans un pays en voie de développement ou dans une région du monde que vous ne connaissez pas, ne prenez pas le possible choc culturel à le légère.
reference: If traveling in a developing country for the first time – or in a new part of the world – don't underestimate the potential culture shock.
translation: If you travel for the first time in a developing country or a region of the world that you don't know, don't take the shock of cultural shock to the slightest.

source: Nombreux sont les voyageurs stables et compétents qui ont été dépassés par la nouveauté des voyages dans les pays en développement, où de nombreux petits ajustements culturels peuvent vite s'accumuler.
reference: Many a stable, capable traveler has been overcome by the newness of developing world travel, where many little cultural adjustments can add up quickly.
translation: Many travelers who have been in developing countries have been overcome by the newness of travel in developing countries, where many small cultural adjustments can quickly accumulate.

source: Surtout au début, pensez à faire des folies dans les hôtels, la nourriture et les services de style et de qualité occidentaux pour vous aider à vous acclimater.
reference: Especially in your initial days, consider splurging on Western-style and -quality hotels, food, and services to help acclimatize.
translation: In particular, think about indulging in the luxury hotels, food and services of Western style and quality, and try to get used to them.

source: Ne dormez pas sur un matelas ou sur un coussin à même le sol dans les zones où vous ne connaissez pas la faune locale.
reference: Do not sleep on a mattress or pad on the ground in areas where you do not know the local fauna.
translation: Don't sleep on a mattress or on a blanket on the ground where you don't know the local fauna.

source: Si vous allez camper, apportez un lit de camp ou un hamac pour vous tenir à l'écart des serpents, scorpions et autres.
reference: If you are going to camp out, bring a camp cot or hammock to keep you away from snakes, scorpions and such.
translation: If you are going camping, bring a sleeping bag or a tent to keep you out of the snakes, scorpions and other animals.

source: Emplissez votre maison avec l'arôme d'un café intense le matin et le soir, avec celui d'une relaxante tisane à la camomille.
reference: Fill your home with a rich coffee in the morning and some relaxing chamomile tea at night.
translation: The morning and evening, you can enjoy a strong coffee with a relaxing tea, with a chamomile tea.

source: Lorsque vous êtes en séjour, vous avez le temps de vous faire plaisir et de prendre quelques minutes supplémentaires pour préparer quelque chose de spécial.
reference: When you're on a staycation, you have the time to treat yourself and take a few extra minutes to brew up something special.
translation: When you are in a hotel, you have the time to indulge in a little bit of luxury and take a few minutes to make something special.

source: Si vous vous sentez d'humeur plus aventureuse, profitez de l'occasion pour préparer un jus ou mélanger des smoothies :
reference: If you're feeling more adventurous, take the opportunity to juice or blend up some smoothies:
translation: If you feel more adventurous, enjoy the opportunity to make a smoothie or mix up a juice.

source: peut-être découvrirez-vous une boisson simple que vous pourrez préparer pour votre petit déjeuner lorsque vous retournerez à votre routine quotidienne.
reference: maybe you'll discover a simple beverage that you can make for breakfast when you're back to your daily routine.
translation: Maybe you will find a simple drink you can make for your breakfast when you return to your normal routine.

source: Si vous vivez dans une ville où la culture de la boisson est variée, allez dans les bars ou les pubs des quartiers que vous ne fréquentez pas.
reference: If you live in a city with a varied drinking culture, go to bars or pubs in neighborhoods you don't frequent.
translation: If you live in a city where the culture of drinking is varied, go to bars or pubs in the areas you don't frequent.

source: Pour ceux qui ne connaissent pas bien le jargon médical, les mots « infectieux » et « contagieux » ont un sens distinct.
reference: For those unfamiliar with medical jargon, the words infectious and contagious have distinct meanings.
translation: For those who don't know the jargon in medical jargon, the words " infectious" and " contagious" have distinct meanings.

source: Une maladie infectieuse est celle causée par un agent pathogène, tel qu'un virus, une bactérie, un champignon ou d’autres parasites.
reference: An infectious disease is one that is caused by a pathogen, such as a virus, bacterium, fungus or other parasites.
translation: A disease is one that is caused by an infectious agent, such as a virus, a bacterium, a fungus, or other parasites.

source: Une maladie contagieuse est une maladie facilement transmissible lorsqu’on se trouve à proximité d’une personne infectée.
reference: A contagious disease is a disease which is easily transmitted by being in the vicinity of an infected person.
translation: A contagious disease is a disease easily transmitted when you are near someone infected.

source: De nombreux gouvernements exigent que les visiteurs qui entrent dans leur pays ou les résidents qui le quittent soient vaccinés contre toute une série de maladies.
reference: Many governments require visitors entering, or residents leaving, their countries to be vaccinated for a range of diseases.
translation: Many governments require visitors entering their country or residents leaving their country to be vaccinated against a variety of diseases.

source: Ces exigences peuvent souvent dépendre des pays visités par un voyageur, ou qu'il compte visiter.
reference: These requirements may often depend on what countries a traveller has visited or intends to visit.
translation: These requirements may often depend on the country visited by a traveller, or he intends to visit.

source: Un des points forts de Charlotte, en Caroline du Nord, est l'abondance des services de haute qualité pour les familles.
reference: One of strong points of Charlotte, North Carolina, is that it has an abundance of high-quality options for families.
translation: Charlotte, North Carolina, has a number of high quality services for families.

source: Les résidents d’autres régions citent souvent la convivialité familiale comme raison principale de leur installation, et les visiteurs trouvent souvent la ville facile à apprécier avec des enfants à côté.
reference: Residents from other areas often cite family-friendliness as a primary reason for moving there, and visitors often find the city easy to enjoy with children around.
translation: Other regions cite the conviviality of family as the main reason for their installation, and visitors often find the city easy to enjoy with children in the backyard.

source: Au cours des 20 dernières années, le nombre d'options adaptées aux enfants dans le quartier des affaires de Charlotte a connu une croissance exponentielle.
reference: In the past 20 years, the amount of child-friendly options in Uptown Charlotte has grown exponentially.
translation: The number of child-friendly options in Charlotte's district of the business district has grown exponentially over the past 20 years.

source: En général, les familles n’utilisent pas de taxis à Charlotte, bien que ces derniers puissent se révéler utiles dans certaines circonstances.
reference: Taxis are not generally used by families in Charlotte, though they can be of some use in certain circumstances.
translation: Generally speaking, families don't use taxis in Charlotte, though they can be useful in certain circumstances.

source: Il y a une surtaxe pour avoir plus de deux passagers, donc cette option pourrait être plus coûteuse qu'indispensable.
reference: There is a surcharge for having more than 2 passengers, so this option might be more expensive than necessary.
translation: There is a surcharge for having more than two passengers, so this option may be more expensive than necessary.

source: L’Antarctique, qui entoure le pôle Sud, est l’endroit le plus froid sur Terre.
reference: Antarctica is the coldest place on Earth, and surrounds the South Pole.
translation: The Antarctic, which surrounds the South Pole, is the coldest place on Earth.

source: Les visites touristiques sont coûteuses, exigent une bonne condition physique, ne peuvent avoir lieu qu'en été (de novembre à février) et sont largement limitées à la péninsule, aux îles, et à la mer de Ross.
reference: Tourist visits are costly, demand physical fitness, can only take place in summer Nov-Feb, and are largely limited to the Peninsula, Islands and Ross Sea.
translation: Tourist visits are expensive, require good physical condition, can only be made in summer (November to February), and are generally limited to the Peninsula, the islands, and the Ross Sea.

source: Quelques milliers d'employés vivent ici en été dans une quarantaine de bases, principalement dans ces régions ; un petit nombre d'entre eux restent en hiver.
reference: A couple of thousand staff live here in summer in some four dozen bases mostly in those areas; a small number stay over winter.
translation: Some of the workers live here in summer in a dozen bases, mainly in these regions; a small number stay in winter.

source: L'Antarctique intérieur est un plateau désolé recouvert de 2 à 3 km de glace.
reference: Inland Antarctica is a desolate plateau covered by 2-3 km of ice.
translation: The Antarctic interior is a desolate plateau covered with 2-3 km of ice.

source: Expéditions aériennes spécifiques et ponctuelles vers l’intérieur des terres, pour l’alpinisme ou pour atteindre le Pôle, disposant d’une vaste base.
reference: Occasional specialist air tours go inland, for mountaineering or to reach the Pole, which has a large base.
translation: Aircraft cargoes and expeditions to the interior of the country, for climbing or reaching the Pole, with a large base.

source: L'autoroute du pôle Sud est une route de 1 600 km entre la station de McMurdo, au bord de la mer de Ross, et le pôle.
reference: The South Pole Traverse (or Highway) is a 1600 km trail from McMurdo Station on the Ross Sea to the Pole.
translation: The South Pole Highway is a 1,600 km road between McMurdo Station, in the Ross Sea, and the Pole.

source: Il s'agit de neige compactée, avec des crevasses comblées et marquées par des fanions. Il ne peut être parcouru que par des tracteurs spécialisés, tirant des traîneaux transportant carburant et fournitures.
reference: It's compacted snow with crevasses filled in and marked by flags. It can only be traveled by specialized tractors, hauling sleds with fuel and supplies.
translation: It is snow compacted, with crevasses filled and marked by fanions. It can only be traveled by specialized tractors, pulling heavy trailers carrying fuel and supplies.

source: Ces derniers ne sont pas très agiles, de sorte que la piste doit faire une longue embardée autour des montagnes transantarctiques pour arriver sur le plateau.
reference: These aren't very nimble so the trail has to take a long swerve around the Transantarctic Mountains to come onto the plateau.
translation: These are not very agile, so the track must make a long trek around the Transantarctic Mountains to reach the plateau.

source: En hiver, la cause d’accidents la plus fréquente est le caractère glissant des routes, des trottoirs et surtout des marches.
reference: The most common cause for accidents in winter is slippery roads, pavements (sidewalks) and especially steps.
translation: In winter, the most common cause of accidents is the tendency of the pavement, the tracks and especially the steps to slide.

source: Des chaussures avec des semelles adéquates, c'est le minimum. Les chaussures d'été glissent très souvent sur la glace et sur la neige, même certains modèles prévus pour l'hiver n'y dérogent pas.
reference: At a minimum, you need footwear with suitable soles. Summer shoes are usually very slippery on ice and snow, even some winter boots are deficient.
translation: French: A proper footwear is essential, even in winter. The summer shoes slip easily on the ice and snow, even some winter boots do not.

source: Le motif doit être suffisamment profond, soit 5 mm (1/5 po) ou plus, et le matériau doit être suffisamment souple par temps froid.
reference: The pattern should be deep enough, 5 mm (1/5 inch) or more, and the material soft enough in cold temperatures.
translation: The pattern should be deep enough, 5 mm (1/5 in) or more, and the material should be soft enough for cold weather.

source: Certaines bottes sont munies de crampons et il existe un équipement complémentaire à crampons pour les conditions glissantes, qui convient à la plupart des chaussures et des bottes, pour les talons ou les talons et la semelle.
reference: Some boots have studs and there is studded add-on equipment for slippery conditions, suitable for most shoes and boots, for the heels or heels and sole.
translation: Some boots have crampons and there is a supplemental crampon for conditions with glide, which is suitable for most boots and boots, for the heels or the heels and the sole.

source: Les talons doivent être bas et larges. Du sable, du gravier ou du sel (chlorure de calcium) est souvent dispersé sur les routes ou les chemins pour améliorer la traction.
reference: Heels should be low and wide. Sand, gravel or salt (calcium chloride) is often scattered on roads or paths to improve traction.
translation: The shoes should be wide and wide. Sand, gravel or salt (calcium chloride) is often spread on the roads or paths to improve traction.

source: Les avalanches ne sont pas des phénomènes anormaux ; les pentes escarpées ne peuvent retenir qu'une petite quantité de neige, dont l'excédent se répand sous forme d'avalanche.
reference: Avalanches are not an abnormality; steep slopes can hold only so much slow, and the excess volumes will come down as avalanches.
translation: The avalanches are not abnormal phenomena; the slopes are steep enough to hold only a small amount of snow, which is deposited as avalanches.

source: Le problème est que la neige colle, alors si elle s'effondre, c'est qu'il y a eu un élément déclencheur. Or, un léger effondrement de la neige peut être le déclencheur pour tout le reste.
reference: The problem is that snow is sticky, so it needs some triggering to come down, and some snow coming down can be the triggering event for the rest.
translation: The problem is that snow falls, so if it falls, it's because there was a triggering element. So, a slight fall of snow can be the triggering element for all the rest.

source: Parfois, l'élément déclencheur est le réchauffement solaire sur la neige, parfois c'est juste davantage de neige, et d'autres fois il peut s'agir d'événements naturels ou de l'activité humaine.
reference: Sometimes the original trigging event is the sun warming the snow, sometimes some more snowfall, sometimes other natural events, often a human.
translation: Sometimes the triggering factor is the sun warming on the snow, sometimes it is just more snow, and sometimes it can be natural or human activity.

source: Une tornade est un tourbillon d'air à basse-pression en forme de colonne, l'air alentour est aspiré vers l'intérieur et le haut.
reference: A tornado is a spinning column of very low-pressure air, which sucks the surrounding air inward and upward.
translation: Tornadoes are a low pressure air mass in a column form, the air around it is sucked in and upward.

source: Ils génèrent des vents violents (souvent de 100 à 200 miles/heure) et peuvent soulever des objets lourds dans les airs, les transportant au fur et à mesure que la tornade se déplace.
reference: They generate high winds (often 100-200 miles/hour) and can lift heavy objects into the air, carrying them as the tornado moves.
translation: They generate violent winds (often 100-200 miles/hr) and can lift heavy objects in the air, moving them as the storm moves.

source: Elles commencent comme des entonnoirs descendant des nuages orageux, et deviennent des « tornades » lorsqu’elles touchent terre.
reference: They begin as funnels descending from storm clouds, and become "tornadoes" when they touch the ground.
translation: They begin as a series of descending clouds, and become tornadoes when they touch the ground.

source: Les fournisseurs de VPN (réseau privé virtuel) personnels sont un excellent moyen de contourner à la fois la censure politique et le géofiltrage IP commercial.
reference: Personal VPN (virtual private network) providers are an excellent way of circumventing both political censorship and commercial IP-geofiltering.
translation: Personal VPN (virtual private network) providers are a great way to circumvent both political censorship and IP geofiltering.

source: Ils sont supérieurs aux proxy web pour plusieurs raisons : ils redirigent tout le trafic en ligne, pas seulement le http.
reference: They are superior to web proxies for several reasons: They re-route all Internet traffic, not only http.
translation: They are superior to proxy websites for several reasons: they redirect all the traffic in the web, not only the http.

source: Ils offrent normalement une plus grande largeur de bande et une meilleure qualité de service. Elles sont cryptées et donc plus difficiles à espionner.
reference: They normally offer higher bandwidth and better quality of service. They are encrypted and thus harder to spy on.
translation: They usually offer a wider band and better service quality. They are encrypted and therefore harder to spy on.

source: Les entreprises de médias mentent couramment sur l'objectif de cette mesure, prétendant qu'elle vise à « empêcher le piratage ».
reference: The media companies routinely lie about the purpose of this, claiming that it is to "prevent piracy".
translation: The media companies often lie about the purpose of this measure, claiming it is to "prevent piracy".

source: En fait, les codes régionaux n'ont absolument aucun effet sur la copie illégale; une copie bit à bit d'un disque fonctionne très bien sur n'importe quel appareil où l'original peut être joué.
reference: In fact, region codes have absolutely no effect on illegal copying; a bit-for-bit copy of a disk will play just fine on any device where the original will.
translation: In fact, the regional codes have no effect on illegal copying; a copy of a disk works very well on any device where the original can be played.

source: Le but réel est de donner à ces entreprises un plus grand contrôle sur leurs marchés ; il s’agit de gagner de l’argent.
reference: The actual purpose is to give those companies more control over their markets; it's all about money spinning.
translation: The real goal is to give these companies a greater control over their markets; it is to gain money.

source: Les appels étant acheminés par l'internet, vous n'avez pas besoin d'utiliser une compagnie de téléphone située où vous vivez ou où vous voyagez.
reference: Because calls are routed over the Internet, you do not need to use a phone company located where you live or where you travel.
translation: The telephone calls are being sent by the internet, so you don't need a telephone company that is located where you live or where you travel.

source: Il n’est pas non plus obligatoire d’obtenir un numéro local de la collectivité dans laquelle vous vivez; vous pouvez obtenir une connexion Internet par satellite dans les contrées sauvages de Chicken, en Alaska, et sélectionner un numéro qui indique que vous êtes dans l’Arizona ensoleillée.
reference: There is also no requirement that you obtain a local number from the community in which you live; you can obtain a satellite Internet connection in the wilds of Chicken, Alaska and select a number which claims you're in sunny Arizona.
translation: It is not mandatory to obtain a local telephone number in your area; you can obtain a satellite Internet connection in remote areas of Chicken, Alaska, and select a number that indicates that you are in Arizona in the sunshine.

source: Souvent, il vous faut acheter un numéro international qui autorise les appels en RCTP. L'endroit où votre numéro de téléphone est localisé est déterminant pour les personnes qui vous appellent.
reference: Often, you have to buy a global number separately that allows PSTN phones to call you. Where the number is from makes a difference for people calling you.
translation: Often, you need to buy a number that allows international calls. The place where your phone is located determines the number that you call.

source: Les applications de traduction en temps réel sont des applis capable de traduire automatiquement des segments entiers de texte, ceci d'une langue vers une autre.
reference: Real-time text translator apps – applications that are capable of automatically translating whole segments of text from one language into another.
translation: Real-time translation applications are applications capable of automatically translating segments of text from one language to another.

source: Certaines des applications de cette catégorie peuvent même traduire des textes en langue étrangère inscrits sur des panneaux ou d'autres objets du quotidien lorsque l'utilisateur pointe son smartphone vers eux.
reference: Some of the applications in this category can even translate texts in foreign languages on signs or other objects in the real world when the user points the smartphone towards those objects.
translation: Some of these applications can even translate text in foreign language on a daily basis when the user points his smartphone to them.

source: Les moteurs de traduction se sont considérablement améliorés, et donnent maintenant souvent des traductions plus ou moins correctes (et plus rarement du charabia), mais il faut faire attention, car ils ont peut-être encore tout faux.
reference: The translation engines have improved dramatically, and now often give more or less correct translations (and more seldom gibberish), but some care is due, as they still may have gotten it all wrong.
translation: The translation engines have improved greatly, and now give more or less correct translations (and sometimes even more or less charabia), but it is important to be careful, because they may still be a bit misleading.

source: L'une des applications les plus réputées dans cette catégorie est Google Translate, qui permet de traduire hors ligne après avoir téléchargé les données linguistiques souhaitées.
reference: One of the most prominent apps in this category is Google Translate, which allows offline translation after downloading the desired language data.
translation: The most popular app in this category is Google Translate, which allows you to translate online after downloading the desired language data.

source: L'utilisation d'applications de navigation par GPS sur votre smartphone peut être le moyen le plus simple et le plus pratique pour vos déplacements en dehors de votre pays de résidence.
reference: Using GPS navigation apps on your smartphone can be the easiest and most convenient way to navigate when out of your home country.
translation: Using GPS navigation apps on your smartphone can be the easiest and most convenient way to travel around the world without your country of citizenship.

source: Il peut permettre d’économiser de l’argent en achetant de nouvelles cartes pour un GPS ou un appareil GPS autonome, ou bien en en louant un auprès d’une société de location de voitures.
reference: It can save money over buying new maps for a GPS, or a standalone GPS device or renting one from a car rental company.
translation: It can save money by buying new GPS or GPS devices or renting one from a car rental company.

source: Si vous n’avez pas de connexion de données sur votre téléphone, ou s’il est hors de portée, ses performances peuvent être limitées ou indisponibles.
reference: If you don't have a data connection for your phone, or when it is out of range, their performance can be limited or unavailable.
translation: If you don't have data connection or you are out of range, your phone performance may be limited or unavailable.

source: Chaque magasin du coin est rempli d'une panoplie déroutante de cartes téléphoniques prépayées qui peuvent être utilisées à partir de téléphones payants ou de téléphones ordinaires.
reference: Every corner store is filled with a confusing array of pre-paid phone cards that can be used from pay phones or ordinary telephones.
translation: Every corner store has a variety of prepaid phone cards that can be used from pay phones or ordinary phones.

source: Si la plupart des cartes permettent d'appeler partout, certaines sont spécialisées dans l'offre de tarifs avantageux pour des groupes de pays spécifiques.
reference: While most cards are good for calling anywhere, some specialise in providing favourable call rates to specific groups of countries.
translation: Most cards allow you to call anywhere in the world, but some specialise in offering special tariffs for specific countries.

source: L’accès à ces services se fait souvent par le biais d’un numéro de téléphone gratuit qui peut être appelé sans frais depuis presque tous les téléphones.
reference: Access to these services is often through a toll-free telephone number that can be called from most phones without charge.
translation: The access to these services is often made available by a free phone number which can be called from almost any mobile phone.

source: Les règles concernant la photographie régulière s'appliquent également à l'enregistrement vidéo, voire même davantage.
reference: Rules regarding regular photography also apply to video recording, possibly even more so.
translation: The rules regarding regular photography apply equally to video recording, even more so.

source: S'il est interdit de prendre une simple photo de quelque chose, il ne faut même pas penser à en enregistrer une vidéo.
reference: If just taking a photo of something isn't allowed, then you shouldn't even think of recording a video of it.
translation: If you take a picture of something, you should not even think about taking a video.

source: Si vous utilisez un drone, vérifiez bien à l'avance ce que vous êtes autorisé à filmer et quels permis ou licences supplémentaires sont nécessaires.
reference: If using a drone, check well in advance as to what you are allowed to film and what permits or additional licensing are required.
translation: If you use a drone, check the license requirements and permits before you start.

source: Faire voler un drone près d’un aéroport ou au-dessus d’une foule est presque toujours une mauvaise idée, même si ce n’est pas illégal dans votre région.
reference: Flying a drone near an airport or over a crowd is almost always a bad idea, even if it's not illegal in your area.
translation: Flying a drone near an airport or above a crowd is almost always a bad idea, even if it's illegal in your area.

source: De nos jours, il est rare que les gens réservent leur vol directement via la compagnie aérienne sans avoir préalablement recherché et comparé les prix.
reference: Nowadays air travel is only rarely booked directly through the airline without first searching and comparing prices.
translation: Today, it is rare for people to book their flight directly from the airline without having previously searched and compared the prices.

source: Un même vol peut parfois présenter de grandes disparités tarifaires entre les agrégateurs ; avant de réserver, il est donc avantageux de comparer les résultats des recherches ainsi que de consulter le site web de la compagnie aérienne elle-même.
reference: Sometimes the same flight can have vastly differing prices at various agregators and it pays to compare search results and to also look at the website of the airline itself before booking.
translation: A same flight may sometimes present large differences in fares between the airlines; before booking, it is therefore advisable to compare the results of the search and the airline itself.

source: Si vous n’avez pas besoin de visa pour des séjours de courte durée dans certains pays en tant que touriste ou pour le voyage d'affaires, le fait d’y aller en tant qu’étudiant étranger nécessite généralement un séjour plus long que celui d’un simple touriste.
reference: While you may not need a visa for short visits to certain countries as a tourist or for business, going there as an international student generally requires a longer stay than going there just as a casual tourist.
translation: If you don't need a visa for a short stay in some countries as tourists or business travelers, you need to go abroad as an international student to have a longer stay than if you were just a tourist.

source: En général, pour séjourner dans un pays étranger sur une longue période, vous devez obtenir au préalable un visa.
reference: In general, staying in any foreign country for an extended period of time will require you to obtain a visa in advance.
translation: Generally, for a long period of time in a foreign country, you must obtain a visa.

source: Les procédures de demande et exigences en matière de visas étudiants sont généralement différentes de celles des visas standard de tourisme ou d'affaires.
reference: Student visas generally have different requirements and application procedures from normal tourist or business visas.
translation: Student visas generally have different requirements and procedures from standard tourist or business visas.

source: Pour la plupart des pays, vous aurez besoin d’une lettre d'acceptation de l’établissement dans lequel vous souhaitez étudier, ainsi que d’une preuve de fonds suffisants pour subvenir à vos besoins au moins pendant la première année de votre cursus.
reference: For most countries, you will need an offer letter from the institution you wish to study at, and also evidence of funds to support yourself for at least the first year of your course.
translation: For most countries, you will need a letter of acceptance from the institution you wish to study, and a proof of funds sufficient to pay for your basic needs for at least the first year of your studies.

source: Pour le détail des conditions, voyez auprès de l’établissement ainsi que du service d’immigration du pays dans lequel vous souhaitez étudier.
reference: Check with the institution, as well as the immigration department for the country you wish to study in for detailed requirements.
translation: For details of the conditions, see the embassy or immigration service in your country where you wish to study.

source: À moins que vous ne soyez un diplomate, travailler à l’étranger signifie généralement que vous devrez remplir la déclaration d’impôts sur le revenu dans le pays où vous êtes basé.
reference: Unless you are a diplomat, working overseas generally means that you will have to file income tax in the country you are based in.
translation: Unless you are a diplomat, working abroad means that you will need to file income tax returns in the country where you are based.

source: L'impôt sur le revenu est structuré différemment dans différents pays, et les taux d'imposition et les tranches d'imposition varient largement d'un pays à l'autre.
reference: Income tax is structured differently in different countries, and the tax rates and brackets vary widely from one country to another.
translation: The tax system in different countries is structured differently, and the tax rates and the brackets vary widely from country to country.

source: Dans certains pays fédéraux tels que les États-Unis et le Canada, l'impôt sur le revenu est prélevé à la fois au niveau fédéral et au niveau local, de sorte que les taux et les tranches d'imposition peuvent varier d'une région à l'autre.
reference: In some federal countries, such as the United States and Canada, income tax is levied both at the federal level and at the local level, so the rates and brackets can vary from region to region.
translation: In some federal countries such as the United States and Canada, income tax is paid both at the federal and local level, so that tax rates and brackets can vary from region to region.

source: Alors que le contrôle de l'immigration est généralement absent ou constitue une formalité à l'arrivée dans votre pays d'origine, le contrôle douanier peut être une source de tracas.
reference: While immigration check is usually absent or a formality when you arrive in your homeland, customs control can be a hassle.
translation: So, when you arrive in your country of origin, you may encounter customs control, which can be a hassle.

source: Assurez-vous de savoir ce que vous pouvez et ne pouvez pas apporter, et déclarez tout ce qui dépasse les limites légales.
reference: Make sure you know what you can and cannot bring in and declare anything over the legal limits.
translation: Check what you can and can't bring, and declare what you can't.

source: Le moyen le plus simple de se lancer dans la rédaction d’articles de voyage est de se perfectionner sur un blogue de voyage bien établi.
reference: The easiest way to get started in the business of travel writing is to hone your skills on an established travel blog website.
translation: The easiest way to start writing travel blogs is to get a good blogging website established.

source: Après, et seulement après avoir maîtrisé le formatage et la révision en ligne, vous pourrez créer votre propre site internet.
reference: After you become comfortable with formatting and editing on the web, then later, you might create your own website.
translation: After that, and only after you have mastered the format and revision in the online format, you can create your own website.

source: Le bénévolat en voyage est un excellent moyen de faire une différence, mais il ne s’agit pas seulement de donner.
reference: Volunteering while travelling is a great way to make a difference but it's not just about giving.
translation: Volunteering abroad is a great way to make a difference, but it isn't just to give.

source: Vivre et faire du bénévolat dans un pays étranger est une excellente façon de découvrir une culture différente, de rencontrer de nouvelles personnes, d'apprendre à se connaître soi-même, à acquérir de nouvelles perspectives et même de nouvelles compétences.
reference: Living and volunteering in a foreign country is a great way to get to know a different culture, meet new people, learn about yourself, get a sense of perspective and even gain new skills.
translation: Living and volunteering abroad is a great way to learn a different culture, meet new people, acquire new perspectives and even new skills.

source: Cela peut également être un bon moyen d'étirer un budget pour permettre un séjour plus long quelque part, car de nombreux emplois de bénévoles offrent le gîte et le couvert et certains versent un petit salaire.
reference: It can also be a good way to stretch a budget to allow a longer stay somewhere since many volunteer jobs provide room and board and a few pay a small salary.
translation: This can also be a good way to stretch a budget for a longer stay somewhere, because many volunteer jobs offer accommodation and some pay a small salary.

source: Les Vikings ont utilisé les voies navigables russes pour atteindre la mer Noire et la mer Caspienne. Certaines parties de ces itinéraires peuvent toujours être utilisées. Vérifiez la nécessité éventuelle de permis spéciaux, qui peuvent être difficiles à obtenir.
reference: Vikings used the Russian waterways to get to the Black Sea and Caspian Sea. Parts of these routes can still be used. Check possible need for special permits, which may be difficult to get.
translation: The Vikings used the Russian channels to reach the Black Sea and the Caspian Sea. Some of these routes can still be used. Check the need for special permits, which can be difficult to obtain.

source: Le canal de la mer Blanche relie l'océan Arctique à la mer Baltique, via le lac Onega, le lac Ladoga et Saint-Pétersbourg, passant principalement par les rivières et les lacs.
reference: The White Sea–Baltic Canal connects the Arctic Ocean to the Baltic Sea, via Lake Onega, Lake Ladoga and Saint Petersburg, mostly by rivers and lakes.
translation: The canal of the Sea Blanche connects the Arctic Ocean to the Baltic Sea via the Onega, Ladoga and Saint-Pétersbourg rivers and lakes.

source: Le lac Onega est également relié à la Volga, de sorte qu'il est encore possible de venir de la mer Caspienne en passant par la Russie.
reference: Lake Onega is also connected to Volga, so coming from the Caspian Sea through Russia is still possible.
translation: The Onega Lake is also connected to the Volga, so that you can still come from the Caspian Sea by crossing the Russian border.

source: Rassurez-vous : une fois que vous aurez atteint les ports de plaisance, tout sera clair. Vous rencontrerez d'autres auto-stoppeurs, qui vous feront part de leurs informations.
reference: Be assured that once you hit the marinas everything will be pretty obvious. You will meet other boat hitchhikers and they will share their information with you.
translation: Thank you for your patience: Once you reach the port of plaisance, everything will be clear. You will meet other motorists, who will tell you about their information.

source: Fondamentalement, vous afficherez des annonces pour proposer votre aide, arpenterez les quais, aborderez les personnes nettoyant leurs yachts, essayerez de faire connaissance avec des navigateurs au bar, etc.
reference: Basically you'll be putting up notices offering your help, pacing the docks, approaching people cleaning their yachts, trying to make contact with sailors in the bar, etc.
translation: Basically, you will display ads to offer your help, walk the quais, approach the people cleaning their yachts, try to meet with a sailor, etc.

source: Essayez de parler au plus grand nombre de personnes possible. Au bout d’un certain temps, tout le monde vous connaîtra et vous donnera des indications sur le bateau qui cherche quelqu’un.
reference: Try to talk to as many people as possible. After a while everyone will know you and will give you hints as to which boat is looking for someone.
translation: Try to speak to the most people possible. At some point, everyone will know you and will give you hints on the boat that is looking for someone.

source: Vous devez choisir avec soin votre compagnie aérienne Frequent Flyer dans le cadre d'une alliance.
reference: You should choose your Frequent Flyer airline in an alliance carefully.
translation: You must choose carefully your airline carrier in the context of a alliance.

source: Même si vous pensez qu’il est intuitif de rejoindre la compagnie aérienne avec laquelle vous voyagez le plus, vous devez savoir que les privilèges offerts sont souvent différents et que le système de points de fidélité peut être plus généreux avec une autre compagnie de la même alliance.
reference: Although you may think it is intuitive to join the airline you fly most, you should be aware that privileges offered are often different and frequent flyer points may be more generous under a different airline in the same alliance.
translation: Even if you think that it's intuitively intuitive to join the airline with which you travel the most, you must know that the privileges offered are often different and that the loyalty system can be more generous with a different airline of the same alliance.

source: Les compagnies aériennes telles que Airlines such as Emirates, Etihad Airways, Qatar Airways et Turkish Airlines ont grandement développé leur offres en Afrique, et offrent des liaisons vers les villes africaines majeures à des tarifs compétitifs comparés aux autres compagnies aériennes européennes.
reference: Airlines such as Emirates, Etihad Airways, Qatar Airways & Turkish Airlines have greatly expanded their services to Africa, and offer connections to many major African cities at competitive rates than other European airlines.
translation: Airlines such as Emirates, Etihad Airways, Qatar Airways and Turkish Airlines have greatly developed their offerings in Africa, and offer excellent fares to major African cities to competitive rates compared to other European airlines.

source: En 2014 la compagnie Turkish Airlines dessert 39 destinations dans 30 pays d'Afrique.
reference: Turkish Airlines flies to 39 destinations in 30 African countries as of 2014.
translation: Turkish Airlines flies to 39 destinations in 30 African countries in 2014.

source: Si vous avez plus de temps pour voyager, comparez le prix total du billet vers l'Afrique avec le prix d'un billet pour faire le tour du monde.
reference: If you have additional travel time, check to see how your total fare quote to Africa compares with a round-the-world fare.
translation: If you have more time to travel, compare the total cost of the trip to Africa with the cost of a round-the-world trip.

source: N'oubliez pas d'ajouter les frais supplémentaires de visas, de taxes de départ, de transport terrestre, etc. pour tous ces endroits en dehors de l'Afrique.
reference: Don't forget to add in the extra costs of additional visas, departure taxes, ground transportation, etc. for all those places outside of Africa.
translation: Don't forget to add extra fees for visas, taxes of departure, transportation, etc. for these places outside of Africa.

source: Si vous voulez faire le tour du monde en avion en restant uniquement dans l'hémisphère sud, le choix des vols et des destinations sera limité à cause du manque de routes transocéaniques.
reference: If you want to fly around the world completely in the Southern Hemisphere, the choice of flights and destinations is limited due to the lack of transoceanic routes.
translation: If you want to fly around the world in a plane only in the South Pole, the choice of flights and destinations will be limited because of the lack of transoceanic routes.

source: Il n’existe aucune alliance de compagnies aériennes couvrant les jonctions des trois océans de l’hémisphère sud (et SkyTeam ne couvre aucune d’entre elles).
reference: No airline alliance covers all three ocean crossings in the Southern Hemisphere (and SkyTeam covers none of the crossings).
translation: There is no airline alliance covering the three oceans of the South Atlantic (and SkyTeam does not cover any of them).

source: Cependant, Star Alliance couvre tout sauf le Pacifique Sud oriental de Santiago du Chili à Tahiti, qui est un vol LATAM Oneworld.
reference: However, Star Alliance covers everything except the eastern South Pacific from Santiago de Chile to Tahiti, which is a LATAM Oneworld flight.
translation: However, Star Alliance covers all except the Pacific South oriental of Santiago de Chile to Tahiti, which is a LATAM Oneworld flight.

source: Ce vol n’est pas la seule option si vous voulez éviter le Pacifique Sud et la côte ouest de l’Amérique du Sud. (voir ci-dessous)
reference: This flight is not the only option if you want to skip the South Pacific and the west coast of South America. (see below)
translation: This flight is not the only option if you want to avoid the Pacific South and the west coast of the United States. (see below)

source: En 1994, la région azerbaïdjanaise du Haut-Karabakh, ethniquement arménienne, a mené une guerre contre les Azéris.
reference: In 1994, the ethnically Armenian Nagorno-Karabakh region of Azerbaijan waged war against the Azeris.
translation: In 1994, the region of Azerbaijan's Karabakh ethnic group, ethnically Armenian, fought against Azeris.

source: Avec le soutien de l'Arménie, une nouvelle république a été créée. Cependant, aucune nation établie, pas même l'Arménie, ne la reconnaît officiellement.
reference: With Armenian backing, a new republic was created. However, no established nation - not even Armenia - officially recognizes it.
translation: With the support of Armenia, a new republic has been created. However, no nation established, not even Armenia, recognizes officially the new state.

source: Les incidents diplomatiques sur la région continuent d'entacher les relations entre l'Arménie et l'Azerbaïdjan.
reference: Diplomatic arguments over the region continue to mar relations between Armenia and Azerbaijan.
translation: Diplomatic incidents in the region continue to jeopardize relations between Armenia and Azerbaijan.

source: Le quartier du canal (Grachtengordel en néerlandais) est le célèbre quartier du XVIIe siècle qui entoure la Binnenstad d'Amsterdam.
reference: The Canal District (Dutch: Grachtengordel) is the famous 17th-century district surrounding the Binnenstad of Amsterdam.
translation: The canal district (Grachtengordel in Dutch) is the famous 17th century district in the city of Amsterdam that surrounds the Binnenstad.

source: Tout le quartier est inscrit au patrimoine mondial de l'UNESCO pour sa valeur culturelle et historique unique, et les prix de l'immobilier y sont parmi les plus élevés du pays.
reference: The whole district is designated as a UNESCO World Heritage Site for its unique cultural and historical value, and its property values are among the highest of the country.
translation: The whole area is listed on UNESCO's World Heritage List for its unique cultural and historical value, and the prices of the real estate are among the highest in the country.

source: Cinque Terre, qui signifie Cinq Terres, comprend les cinq petits villages côtiers de Riomaggiore, Manarola, Corniglia, Vernazza et Monterosso dans la région italienne de la Ligurie.
reference: Cinque Terre, which means Five Lands, comprises the five small coastal villages of Riomaggiore, Manarola, Corniglia, Vernazza and Monterosso located in the Italian region of Liguria.
translation: Cinque Terre, meaning Five Lands, includes the five small villages of Riomaggiore, Manarola, Corniglia, Vernazza and Monterosso in the Liguria region of Italy.

source: Ils sont inscrits sur la liste du patrimoine mondial de l’UNESCO.
reference: They are listed on the UNESCO World Heritage List.
translation: They are listed on the UNESCO World Heritage List.

source: Au fil des siècles, les gens ont soigneusement construit des terrasses sur le paysage accidenté et escarpé jusqu'aux falaises qui surplombent la mer.
reference: Over the centuries, people have carefully built terraces on the rugged, steep landscape right up to the cliffs that overlook the sea.
translation: Over the centuries, people have carefully built terraces on the rough and unpleasant landscape, which rises to the sea.

source: Une partie de son charme réside dans l'absence de développement visible des entreprises. Des chemins, des trains et des bateaux relient les villages, et les voitures en provenance de l'extérieur ne peuvent y accéder.
reference: Part of its charm is the lack of visible corporate development. Paths, trains and boats connect the villages, and cars cannot reach them from the outside.
translation: His charm lies in the lack of visible development of companies. The roads, trains and boats connect the villages, and cars from outside cannot reach them.

source: Les variantes du français pratiquées en Belgique et en Suisse diffèrent légèrement du français parlé en France, bien qu'elles soient suffisamment similaires pour être mutuellement intelligibles.
reference: The varieties of French which are spoken in Belgium and Switzerland differ slightly from the French spoken in France, though they are similar enough to be mutually intelligible.
translation: The variants of French spoken in Belgium and Switzerland are slightly different from the French spoken in France, but sufficiently similar to be mutually intelligible.

source: Le système de numérotation de la Belgique et de la Suisse francophones présente notamment quelques petites particularités qui diffèrent du français parlé en France, et la prononciation de certains mots est légèrement différente.
reference: In particular, the numbering system in French-speaking Belgium and Switzerland has some slight peculiarities that are different from the French spoken in France, and the pronunciation of some words is slightly different.
translation: The Belgian and Swiss francophone system has also some slight peculiarities that are different from the French spoken in France, and the pronunciation of some words is slightly different.

source: Néanmoins, tous les Belges et les Suisses francophones auraient appris le français standard à l'école, de sorte qu'ils seraient en mesure de vous comprendre même si vous utilisiez le système de numérotation français standard.
reference: Nevertheless, all French-speaking Belgians and Swiss would have learned standard French in school, so they would be able to understand you even if you used the standard French numbering system.
translation: However, all Belgian and Swiss francophones would have learned French standard at school, so that they would be able to understand even if you used the standard French numing system.

source: Dans de nombreuses régions du monde, faire un signe de la main est un geste amical signifiant « bonjour ».
reference: In many parts of the world, waving is a friendly gesture, indicating "hello."
translation: In many parts of the world, gesturing with a hand is a friendly gesture indicating "hello".

source: En revanche, en Malaisie, du moins chez les Malais des zones rurales, cela signifie « viens par ici », comme le fait de plier l'index vers soi, geste utilisé dans certains pays occidentaux, et il ne devrait être utilisé qu'en ce sens.
reference: However, in Malaysia, at least among the Malays in rural areas, it means "come over," similar to the index finger bent toward the body, a gesture which is used in certain Western countries, and should be used only for that purpose.
translation: However, in Malaysia, in particular among the Malays in the rural areas, it means "come here", as the way to fold one's index to one's side, as used in some Western countries, and it should be used only in this sense.

source: De même, un voyageur britannique en Espagne pourrait confondre un signe d'adieu fait par une personne qui tourne la paume de sa main vers elle-même (plutôt que vers la personne à qui elle adresse le signe) avec une invitation à revenir.
reference: Similarly, a British traveller in Spain may mistake a wave goodbye involving the palm facing the waver (rather than the person being waved at) as a gesture to come back.
translation: The same can be said of a British traveller in Spain, who may mistake a sign of farewell made by a person who turns his hand to himself (rather than to the person who is sending the sign) for a request to return.

source: Les langues auxiliaires sont des langues, artificielles ou construites, créées dans le but de faciliter la communication entre des peuples qui, autrement, auraient des difficultés à communiquer.
reference: Auxiliary languages are artificial or constructed languages created with the intent of facilitating communication between peoples who would otherwise have difficulty communicating.
translation: Auxiliary languages are artificial or constructed languages, created to facilitate communication between peoples who otherwise would have difficulty communicating.

source: Elles sont distinctes des langues véhiculaires, qui sont des langues naturelles ou organiques qui deviennent dominantes pour une raison ou une autre en tant que moyen de communication entre les locuteurs d'autres langues.
reference: They are separate from lingua francas, which are natural or organic languages that become dominant for one reason or another as means of communication between speakers of other languages.
translation: They are distinct from the languages of the world, which are natural or organic languages that become dominant in a way or another as a means of communication between the speakers of other languages.

source: Avec la chaleur de la journée, les voyageurs peuvent apercevoir des mirages qui donnent l'illusion de l'eau (ou d'autres choses).
reference: In the heat of the day, travelers can experience mirages that give the illusion of water (or other things).
translation: With the heat of the day, tourists can see mirages that appear to be water (or other things).

source: Celles-ci peuvent être dangereuses si le voyageur poursuit le mirage, gaspillant ainsi une énergie précieuse et l’eau restante.
reference: These can be dangerous if the traveler pursue the mirage, wasting precious energy and remaining water.
translation: These can be dangerous if the traveler continues the mirage, wasting precious energy and remaining water.

source: Même le plus chaud des déserts peut devenir extrêmement froid la nuit. L'hypothermie est un risque réel si vous n'avez pas de vêtements chauds.
reference: Even the hottest of deserts can become extremely cold at night. Hypothermia is a real risk without warm clothing.
translation: Even the coldest of the deserts can become extremely cold the night. Hypothermia is a real risk if you don't have warm clothing.

source: C'est surtout en été qu'il vous faudra faire attention aux moustiques si vous comptez faire de la randonnée en forêt tropicale.
reference: In summer, especially, you'll need to watch out for mosquitoes if you decide to hike through the rainforest.
translation: In summer, especially, you will need to be very careful if you plan to hike in the tropical rainforest.

source: Même si vous conduisez dans la forêt tropicale, quelques secondes avec les portes ouvertes pendant que vous montez dans le véhicule suffisent pour que les moustiques montent dans le véhicule avec vous.
reference: Even if you're driving through the subtropical rainforest, a few seconds with the doors open while you get inside the vehicle is enough time for mosquitoes to get in the vehicle with you.
translation: Even if you drive in the tropical forest, a few seconds with the doors open while you are on the vehicle will let the mosquitoes get in with you.

source: La grippe aviaire, ou de manière plus formelle l'influenza aviaire, peut infecter à la fois les oiseaux et les mammifères.
reference: Bird flu, or more formally avian influenza, can infect both birds and mammals.
translation: The bird flu, or more formally the avian influenza, can infect both birds and mammals.

source: Moins d'un millier de cas ont été rapportés chez les humains, mais certains ont été mortels.
reference: Fewer than a thousand cases have ever been reported in humans, but some of them have been fatal.
translation: Less than a thousand cases have been reported in humans, but some have been fatal.

source: La plupart impliquaient des personnes qui travaillent avec des volailles, mais il existe également un certain risque pour les observateurs d'oiseaux.
reference: Most have involved people who work with poultry, but there is also some risk to birdwatchers.
translation: Most of the animals involved were people who worked with poultry, but there is also a risk for birdwatchers.

source: Les fjords et les vallées escarpées qui cèdent soudainement la place à un haut plateau plus ou moins régulier sont typiques de la Norvège.
reference: Typical for Norway are steep fjords and valleys that suddenly give way to a high, more or less even plateau.
translation: The fjords and valleys that suddenly turn into a plateau more or less regular are typical of Norway.

source: Ces plateaux sont souvent appelés « vidde », pour désigner un vaste espace sans arbre, une étendue sans limites.
reference: These plateaus are often referred to as "vidde" meaning a wide, open treeless space, a boundless expanse.
translation: These terraces are often called "vidde", for a wide open space without trees, a land without boundaries.

source: Dans le Rogaland et à Adger, ils sont souvent qualifiés de « hei », ce qui signifie landes déboisées souvent couvertes de bruyère.
reference: In Rogaland and Agder they are usually called "hei" meaning a treeless moorland often covered in heather.
translation: In Rogaland and Adger, they are often referred to as "hei", meaning landes often covered with heather.

source: Les glaciers ne sont pas stables, mais se détachent de la montagne. Cela provoque des fissures, des crevasses, qui peuvent être obscurcies par des ponts de neige.
reference: The glaciers are not stable, but flow down the mountain. This will cause cracks, crevasses, which may be obscured by snow bridges.
translation: Glaciers are not stable, but they break away from the mountain. They cause cracks, crevasses, which can be obscured by snow bridges.

source: Les murs et les toits des grottes de glace peuvent s’effondrer et les fissures se refermer.
reference: The walls and roofs of ice caves can collapse and cracks can get closed.
translation: The walls and roofs of the caves can collapse and cracks will open.

source: Au bord des glaciers, d'immenses blocs se détachent, tombent, et peut-être rebondissent ou roulent en s'éloignant du bord.
reference: At the edge of glaciers huge blocks break loose, fall down and perhaps jump or roll farther from the edge.
translation: In the glaciers, huge blocks fall, fall, and perhaps bounce or roll away from the edge.

source: La saison touristique des stations de montagne culmine généralement pendant l'été indien.
reference: The tourist season for the hill stations generally peaks during the Indian summer.
translation: The summer tourist season in the Indian Alps peaks generally during the summer of the year.

source: Cependant, leur beauté et leur charme évoluent en hiver, avec de nombreuses stations de montagne pourvues de bonnes quantités de neige et proposant des activités telles que le ski et le snowboard.
reference: However, they have a different kind of beauty and charm during winter, with many hill stations receiving healthy amounts of snow and offering activities such as skiing and snowboarding.
translation: However, their beauty and charm are changing in winter, with many mountain stations with good amounts of snow and offering activities such as skiing and snowboarding.

source: Seules quelques compagnies aériennes proposent encore des tarifs de deuil, qui réduisent légèrement le coût des voyages funéraires de dernière minute.
reference: Only a few airlines still offer bereavement fares, which slightly discount the cost of last-minute funeral travel.
translation: Only a few airlines offer funeral fares, which reduce the cost of funeral travel to a minimum.

source: Les compagnies aériennes qui les proposent sont notamment Air Canada, Delta Air Lines, Lufthansa pour les vols en provenance des États-Unis ou du Canada, et WestJet.
reference: Airlines that offer these include Air Canada, Delta Air Lines, Lufthansa for flights originating from the U.S. or Canada, and WestJet.
translation: Airlines that offer them are Air Canada, Delta Air Lines, Lufthansa for flights from the United States or Canada, and WestJet.

source: Dans tous les cas, vous devez réserver par téléphone directement auprès de la compagnie aérienne.
reference: In all cases, you must book by phone directly with the airline.
translation: In all cases, you should reserve your flight directly with the airline.
